document_data.name: House Jysstev
document_data.History: The house backed the [[Jhannivvar]] pretender for the throne of [[Tethyr]] and subsequently lost its riches, living in near poverty. It was forced to sell its assets in [[Athkatla]] and [[Murann]], and move to [[Eshpurta]]. The house remained well ranked, but only through debts of honour.
document_data.Members: * [[Qar Jysstev]], Namarch on the [[Council of Six]] and lord of the house.
